    "Subsequently, we present a multi-modal financial dataset to facilitate a nuanced approach to data interpretation.",
    "Finally, we introduce an extensive set of evaluation benchmark datasets tailored to test the model's performance across diverse financial tasks.",
    "We introduce FinSet, a 20 billion token, high quality dataset we build for financial LLM training.",
    "Fin-Set is acquired based on a collection of large text corpora (2.9 billion documents, making 135 billion tokens; see Table 1) from which we extract financespecific data that we then clean using a careful filtering pipeline.",
    "The datasets are described in Appendix B."
